33:10.405 --> 33:11.406
You know...

33:13.282 --> 33:14.742
It's a real good band.

33:16.744 --> 33:18.246
-Is that what it is?
-Yeah.

33:18.329 --> 33:19.330
Huh.

33:20.039 --> 33:22.583
-So how far did you get?
-About two hours down the road.

33:22.667 --> 33:24.669
Two hours.

33:24.752 --> 33:27.630
Well, I guess that I should be
real insulted or real flattered, huh?

33:27.714 --> 33:30.133
It just took some time, you know,

33:30.216 --> 33:32.927
for it to really sink in
just how good that music was.

33:33.011 --> 33:34.971
Felt like it'd be a shame to miss out.

33:35.054 --> 33:36.222
Well, all right.

33:37.181 --> 33:39.434
-One beer at a time?
-Yeah.

33:47.025 --> 33:48.359
Thank you.

33:48.443 --> 33:49.444
Yeah.

34:36.449 --> 34:37.450
Hey.

34:38.451 --> 34:40.745
-You all right?
-Yeah.

34:40.828 --> 34:44.415
-Yeah. Are you sure?
-Yeah. It's nothing.

34:46.751 --> 34:48.795
Yo, Beth, can I get a beer?

34:48.878 --> 34:50.713
-No causing any trouble.
-All right.

35:11.901 --> 35:13.611
-Sorry.
-Hey, what's the hurry?

35:13.694 --> 35:16.989
-Come dance with me.
-Sorry. Stop, stop. Get off me!

35:58.072 --> 35:59.073
No, no, no.

36:06.831 --> 36:09.709
Hi, ladies, I'm sorry,
someone just got real sick in there.

36:09.792 --> 36:11.002
I'd use the men's room.

36:14.672 --> 36:16.048
-Excuse me.
-Can I help you?

36:16.132 --> 36:18.092
My friend...

36:18.176 --> 36:21.345
I think she might be a little bit sick.
So I'm just gonna go check on her.

36:21.429 --> 36:22.930
I think she went home, buddy.

36:23.014 --> 36:24.974
-She went home?
-Yeah. I think you should, too.

36:25.057 --> 36:28.227
Yeah, I was... She...
Nah, I'm-I'm-- I'm pretty sure.

36:28.311 --> 36:29.937
I think you have the wrong person here.

36:30.021 --> 36:31.063
You wish we did.

36:31.898 --> 36:32.899
Get back.

36:39.322 --> 36:40.615
Eddie

36:43.576 --> 36:44.452
No shots.

36:45.745 --> 36:47.747
Nobody mentioned a guy with her.

36:57.798 --> 36:58.966
Dumbass.

37:00.843 --> 37:03.095
You're so far over your head,
you can't even see the light.

37:03.179 --> 37:05.223
Is that right?

38:41.694 --> 38:42.695
Who are you?

38:44.405 --> 38:45.906
Why are they coming after you?

38:45.990 --> 38:47.908
No. I'm outta here.

38:47.992 --> 38:49.410
You stay where you are.

38:50.328 --> 38:52.580
-Who are they?
-I don't know. I don't know.

38:52.663 --> 38:54.749
I came in here,
and they asked me if I wanted to party,

38:54.832 --> 38:57.668
and then I said no,
and they just, like, freaked out on me.

38:57.752 --> 38:59.670
I don't know.
Chicks can be rough.

38:59.754 --> 39:00.671
Bullshit.

39:05.426 --> 39:07.136
There's more of 'em out there.

39:09.805 --> 39:13.559
And what

39:14.560 --> 39:17.104
I'm just an asshole who couldn't
stay out of trouble, that's all.

39:20.816 --> 39:22.693
I'm gonna ask you one more time, kid.

39:24.070 --> 39:25.363
You tell me who they are.

39:28.783 --> 39:30.159
No? Okay.

39:33.412 --> 39:34.747
No, wait, wait, wait!

39:36.874 --> 39:40.795
If there's more people out there,
people like this...

39:42.004 --> 39:45.383
I mean, you didn't just come in here
to leave me for them. Did you?

39:48.469 --> 39:49.720
You can help me.

39:50.596 --> 39:51.639
Can't you?

39:52.848 --> 39:53.974
You're like them.

39:55.267 --> 39:56.477
Better, even.

40:00.523 --> 40:01.524
Please.

40:04.026 --> 40:07.071
Thank you all very much! See ya next time.

40:17.665 --> 40:18.666
Let's go.

40:18.749 --> 40:22.586
-Just... do exactly what I say.
-Okay.

40:23.337 --> 40:24.338
Easy.

40:25.089 --> 40:26.090
It's okay.

40:34.056 --> 40:35.933
It's okay. It's okay. Go this way.

40:36.600 --> 40:37.685
Stay with me.

40:38.519 --> 40:39.520
Easy.

40:42.690 --> 40:43.899
Excuse me.

40:45.234 --> 40:47.111
-Go, go, go.
-Wait, wait, wait. What What?

40:58.164 --> 41:00.499
-Go! Go now!
-Whoa, whoa, whoa.

41:08.716 --> 41:10.801
Hey! What's your problem, man?

41:10.885 --> 41:13.053
Come on.

41:19.143 --> 41:21.645
Hey, Ringo, you wanna deal
with these assholes?

41:49.965 --> 41:50.925
Get your ass up.

41:59.934 --> 42:02.478
No! No! No! Help me!

42:21.330 --> 42:22.498
Get off of her!

42:31.382 --> 42:32.424
Hey!

42:33.842 --> 42:34.969
Come on.

43:01.328 --> 43:02.288
No, no, no!

43:05.541 --> 43:06.959
Frank!

44:19.615 --> 44:22.201
No. No. No.

44:22.284 --> 44:24.161
Hey, hey, hey...

44:24.244 --> 44:25.829
-I got you.

44:26.497 --> 44:30.209
Get me a rag! Get me a goddamn rag!

44:30.292 --> 44:33.712
-I got you. Okay. Okay. I'm right here.

44:33.796 --> 44:36.590
I'm gonna get you out of here.
I'm gonna get you out of here.

44:46.058 --> 44:47.559
We're being followed.

44:53.065 --> 44:54.566
Look out!

44:59.405 --> 45:00.280
Now what?

45:26.306 --> 45:29.059
No, please. Please just let me go. Please.

45:34.356 --> 45:36.734
Honestly, I don't know
why these people are after me.

45:36.817 --> 45:38.944
Shut up.
Find the closest hospital. Find it now.

45:39.027 --> 45:40.529
-Okay, yeah--
-Let's go!

45:40.612 --> 45:42.364
Okay. Up three blocks,
then left at the light.

45:42.448 --> 45:45.534
Hey, Beth

45:45.617 --> 45:47.327
Yeah.

45:48.412 --> 45:50.247
I know it hurts,
but you're gonna be all right.

45:50.330 --> 45:53.000
-You need to know that.
-Rex. He's alone.

45:53.083 --> 45:54.126
Where's the turn?

45:54.209 --> 45:56.545
-I don't see any goddamn turn!
-It's here! Left here!

46:09.892 --> 46:11.393
Shit. You all right, man?

46:11.477 --> 46:12.936
-Get your hands off me.
-Take it easy.

46:13.020 --> 46:14.772
-You're bleeding--
-I got a woman in the back.

46:14.855 --> 46:16.982
You help her! Hurry, let's go!

46:17.065 --> 46:18.650
-Come on!
-All right.

46:18.734 --> 46:20.527
This is a gunshot wound.
What happened here?

46:20.611 --> 46:22.112
We have to call the cops.
Take it easy.

46:22.196 --> 46:23.739
-No, I'm okay.
-I got you. Don't worry.

46:23.822 --> 46:24.990
I've gotta get home to my kid.

46:25.073 --> 46:26.575
-Gonna take care of you.
-Let me go!

46:26.658 --> 46:28.202
-God damn.
-Grab her legs.

46:28.285 --> 46:29.286
No!

46:29.369 --> 46:31.163
I'm sorry. I am so goddamn sorry.

46:31.246 --> 46:32.247
I gotta get home to Rex.

46:32.331 --> 46:34.625
-I'll call him. He's gonna be okay.
-Please.

46:34.708 --> 46:36.418
-Hey, you can't leave the scene, man.
-Go!

46:36.502 --> 46:38.587
-Stay here! Let's go.
-Take care of her, hear?

46:38.670 --> 46:39.797
You take care of her!

46:39.880 --> 46:41.423
-Go!
-Let's go!

46:47.513 --> 46:48.514
Now what?

47:17.125 --> 47:19.336
This is not what I signed up for.

47:20.671 --> 47:24.341
Find the girl. And whoever she's with.

47:27.511 --> 47:30.389
And you'll tell me where they are,
and you'll keep your people away.

47:30.472 --> 47:33.433
This has gotten too big.
Look at this mess.

47:35.727 --> 47:37.020
Call it a turf war.

47:38.105 --> 47:39.189
It happens.

47:41.233 --> 47:42.442
Thank you, Lieutenant.

47:47.197 --> 47:48.365
You can go now.

47:58.041 --> 47:59.585
It was outside the window.

47:59.668 --> 48:02.296
The girl must have dropped it
when she was trying to get out.

48:06.800 --> 48:09.887
Laptop is in there. It's what you wanted?

48:29.156 --> 48:30.157
Show me.

48:36.872 --> 48:38.749
You didn't say she'd have help.

48:41.919 --> 48:43.045
He was good.

48:44.212 --> 48:45.464
As good as I've seen.

48:48.425 --> 48:51.094
This is someone's dog, let off the leash.

48:53.055 --> 48:55.724
A man this good
won't be that hard to find.

48:56.558 --> 48:58.268
There'll be people who know him...

49:00.103 --> 49:01.688
who care for him...

49:04.066 --> 49:05.442
or who fear him.

49:11.114 --> 49:12.991
And they'll tell me how to find him.

49:34.012 --> 49:36.932
Sweet dreams, asshole.

49:59.079 --> 50:00.247
Thank you.

50:41.121 --> 50:42.456
Will there be more of them?

50:49.004 --> 50:50.130
I hope so.
